translation[10]{c,v,t}:
  6,9,Aur agar hum iss ko farishta tajveez kertay to hum uss ko aadmi hi banatay aur huamray iss fail say phir inn per wohi ashkaal hota jo abb ashkaal ker rahey hain
  6,10,Aur waqaee aap say pehlay jo payghumbar huye hain unn kay sath bhi istehzaa kiya gaya hai. Phir jin logon ney unn say mazaq kiya tha unn ko uss azab ney aa ghera jiss kay tamaskhur uratay thay
  6,11,Aap farma dijiye kay zara zamin mein chalo phiro phir dekh lo kay takzeeb kerney walon ka kiya anjam hua
  6,12,Aap kahiye kay jo kuch aasmano aur zamin mein mojood hai yeh sab kiss ki milkiyat hai aap keh dijiye kay sab Allah hi ki milkiyat hai Allah ney meharbani farmana apney upper laazim farma liya hai tum ko Allah qayamat kay roz jama keray ga iss mein koi shak nahi jin logon ney apney aap ko ghatay mein daala hai so woh eman nahi layen gay
  6,13,Aur Allah hi kay mulk hain woh sab kuch jo raat mein aur din mein rehti hain aur wohi bara sunnay wala bara jannay wala hai
  6,14,Aap kahiye kay kiya Allah kay siwa jo kay aasmanon aur zamin ka peda kerney wala hai aur jo kay khaney ko deta hai aur uss ko koi khaney ko nahi deta aur kissi ko mabood qarar doon aap farma dijiye kay mujh ko yeh hukum hua hai kay sab say pehlay mein islam qabool keroon aur tu mushrikeen mein say hergiz na hona
  6,15,Aap keh dijiye kay mein agar apney rab ka kehna na manon to mein aik baray din kay azab say darta hun
  6,16,Jiss shaks say uss roz woh azab hata diya jaye to uss per Allah ney bara reham kiya aue yeh sareeh kaamyabi hai
  6,17,Aur agar tujh ko Allah Taalaa koi takleef phonchaye to uss ka door kerney wala siwaye Allah Taalaa kay aur koi nahi. Aur agar tujh ko Allah Taalaa koi nafa phonchaye to woh her cheez per poori qudrat rakhney wala hai
  6,18,Aur wohi Allah apney bandon kay upper ghalib hai bar tar hai aur wohi bari hikmat wala aue poori khabar rakhney wala hai